<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="brief-adj">brief <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /briːf/    美 /briːf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>短暂的；简短的；简洁的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>during his brief life
在他短暂的一生中</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’re running out of time, so let’s <strong>be brief</strong>.
我们时间不多了，所以长话短说吧。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-brief">in brief</h3>
<p>1.<strong>简言之；总而言之：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His success was a long story, but in brief, he succeeded after many failures.
他的成功说来话长。但简单地说，经历多次失败后，他成功了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>briefly /'briːfli/ adv   </p></div>